description: [Clips4Sale / Family Therapy] Marsha May (A Daughter's Progress) (04.10.2015) pt.1 What You Need - It's so nice to have my baby girl living with me again. I've been so lonely since the separation. It's strange being a bachelor again, and having Marsha around makes me feel much better. I don't know what happened between her and her Mother, but she's been very well behaved living with me so far, even if she is a little needy... All I know is I'm happy, it's good to feel like a Dad again. I think we're both going to help each other a lot.... pt.2 Thank You Daddy - I can't believe my fucking Dad. He thinks just because I'm fucking Alex that I want to fuck him?!? Well I don't. I'm in love with my brother. It's none of his business what we do together. He's such a creep, he say's we can "work on it." What the fuck does that mean??? I just wish I had somewhere else to go but my Mom hates me and I don't have any friends around here.
